:\\Users\\zerom\\WixossReact\\src\\screens\\BattleScreen.tsx:7697:3\n  7695 |\n  7696 |   // refs を常に最新の関数インスタンスに同期（Rules of Hooks 対応）\n> 7697 |   doPhaseAdvanceRef.current                = doPhaseAdvance;\n       |   ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Cannot update ref during render\n  7698 |   triggerPendingCrashRef.current           = triggerPendingCrash;\n  7699 |   resolveStackNextRef.current              = resolveStackNext;\n  7700 |   checkPowerZeroBanishRef.current          = checkAndBanishPowerZero;","Error: Cannot access refs during render\n\nReact refs are values that are not needed for rendering. Refs should only be accessed outside of render, such as in event handlers or effects. Accessing a ref value (the `current` property) during render can cause your component not to update as expected (https://react.dev/reference/react/useRef).\n\nC:\\Users\\zerom\\WixossReact\\src\\screens\\BattleScreen.tsx:7698:3\n  7696 |   // refs を常に最新の関数インスタンスに同期（Rules of Hooks 対応）\n  7697 |   doPhaseAdvanceRef.current                = doPhaseAdvance;\n> 7698 |   triggerPendingCrashRef.current           = triggerPendingCrash;\n       |   ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Cannot update ref during render\n  7699 |   resolveStackNextRef.current              = resolveStackNext;\n  7700 |   checkPowerZeroBanishRef.current          = checkAndBanishPowerZero;\n  7701 |   checkContMutationsRef.current            = checkAndApplyContMutations;","Error: Cannot access refs during render\n\nReact refs are values that are not needed for rendering. Refs should only be accessed outside of render, such as in event handlers or effects. Accessing a ref value (the `current` property) during render can cause your component not to update as expected (https://react.dev/reference/react/useRef).\n\nC:\\Users\\zerom\\WixossReact\\src\\screens\\BattleScreen.tsx:7699:3\n  7697 |   doPhaseAdvanceRef.current                = doPhaseAdvance;\n  7698 |   triggerPendingCrashRef.current           = triggerPendingCrash;\n> 7699 |   resolveStackNextRef.current              = resolveStackNext;\n       |   ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Cannot update ref during render\n  7700 |   checkPowerZeroBanishRef.current          = checkAndBanishPowerZero;\n  7701 |   checkContMutationsRef.current            = checkAndApplyContMutations;\n  7702 |   resolvePendingSigniBattleRef.current     = resolvePendingSigniBattle;","Error: Cannot access refs during render\n\nReact refs are values that are not needed for rendering. Refs should only be accessed outside of render, such as in event handlers or effects. Accessing a ref value (the `current` property) during render can cause your component not to update as expected (https://react.dev/reference/react/useRef).\n\nC:\\Users\\zerom\\WixossReact\\src\\screens\\BattleScreen.tsx:7700:3\n  7698 |   triggerPendingCrashRef.current           = triggerPendingCrash;\n  7699 |   resolveStackNextRef.current              = resolveStackNext;\n> 7700 |   checkPowerZeroBanishRef.current          = checkAndBanishPowerZero;\n       |   ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ Cannot update ref during render\n  7701 |   checkContMutationsRef.current            = checkAndApplyContMutations;\n  7702 |   resolvePendingSigniBattleRef.current     = resolvePendingSigniBattle;\n  7703 |   resolvePendingLrigAttackRef.current      = resolvePendingLrigAttack;","Error: Cannot access refs during render\n\nReact refs are values that are not needed for rendering. Refs should only be accessed outside of render, such as in event handlers or effects. Accessing a ref value (the `current` property) during render can cause your component not to update as expected (https://react.dev/reference/react/useRef).\n\nC:\\Users\\zerom\\WixossReact\\src\\screens\\BattleScreen.tsx:7701:3\n  7699 |   resolveStackNextRef.current              = resolveStackNext;\n  7700 |   checkPowerZeroBanishRef.current          = checkAndBanishPowerZero;\n> 7701 |   checkContMutationsRef.current            = checkAndApplyContMut